	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On a Dendy, does the APU frame counter give IRQs every 50 or 60 FPS?
<br />
<br />Easiest way to tell is to run Dragon Quest 1 or 2.  If the music plays slower, it's 50FPS.  If it plays at normal speed, it's 60FPS.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
