	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />APU Frame Counter is generated entirely in the CPU. The Dendy CPU runs faster than the PAL NES CPU; the master clock is divided by 15 instead of 16 for compatibility with raster effects in software for the NTSC Famicom.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

